quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  21,42,"Yithi: “Ngubani na onganikhusela ebusuku okanye emini kuSozinceba?” kodwa bona bayayifulathela inkumbulo yeNkosi yabo"
  21,43,"Ingaba banabanye oothixo abanokubakhusela kuThi? Abanawo nje amandla okubakhusela, bengekhe (kwabona) bakhuseleke kuThi"
  21,44,"Nakanye, Thina Sinike ubunewunewu bobomi beli hlabathi kula madoda noyise bawo lada ixesha laya liba lide kubo. Ababoni na bona ukuba siya siwucutha ngokuwucutha umhlaba ngokwemida yawo? Ingaba ngabo na abaza kuba noloyiso"
  21,45,"Yithi (Muhammad): “Mna ndilumkisa kuphela ngesiTyhilelo (esivela kuAllâh) kodwa izithulu aziluva ubizo xa zilunyukiswa"
  21,46,"Ke kaloku xa umfutho (nje) wesohlwayo seNkosi yakho unokubarheca, angekhe bangathi, “Yeha kuthi! Inene, thina besingabenzi bobubi.”"
  21,47,"Ke kaloku Siza kumisela umthetho wokulingana wobulungisa ngoMhla woVuko, yaye akukho bani uza kuphathwa ngokungenabulungisa nangantoni na. Ke kaloku ukuba kuthe kwakho ubunzima (bezenzo ezilungileyo nokuba zezingalunganga) obungangobekhozo lwemostadi. Siya kubuzisa (obo bunzima ngaphambili). Sanele Thina Sisedwa ukufaka embuzweni"
  21,48,"Inene Thina Sanika uMûsâ noHârûn inqobo (yokwahlula phakathi kokulungileyo nokungalunganga), nokukhanya okukhazimlayo nenkumbuzo kumalungisa"
  21,49,"Abo bayoyikayo iNkosi yabo bengaYiboni nokuYibona, bona bayayoyika neYure"
  21,50,Le ‘Kur’ân ngumyalezo osikelelekileyo eSiwuthumele phantsi (emhlabeni). Ingaba niza kuyiphika